    fn suggest_derive(

            

        

            

                1423

                1424

                1425

                1468

                1470

                1471

                1473

                1474
            

            

                
            

            

                
                traits.push(self.tcx.def_span(trait_pred.def_id()));

                1479
            

            

                
            

            

                

            

        

            

                1480

                1490

                1491
            

            

                
            

            

                
            }

            

        

            

                1492
            

            

                
            

            

                
            derives_grouped.push((self_name, self_span, trait_name));

            

        

            

                1493
            

            

                
            

            

                
        }

            

        

            

                1494
            

            

                
            

            

                

            

        

            

                1495

                1496

                1497

                1499
            

            

                
            

            

                
                span,

                1501

                1502

    fn suggest_use_candidates(&self, err: &mut Diagnostic, msg: String, candidates: Vec<DefId>) {

            

        

            

                1547
            

            

                
            

            

                
        let parent_map = self.tcx.visible_parent_map(());

            

        

            

                1548
            

            

                
            

            

                

            

        

            

                1549
            

            

                
            

            

                
        // Separate out candidates that must be imported with a glob, because they are named `_`

            

        

            

                1550
            

            

                
            

            

                
        // and cannot be referred with their identifier.

            

        

            

                1551
            

            

                
            

            

                
        let (candidates, globs): (Vec<_>, Vec<_>) = candidates.into_iter().partition(|trait_did| {

            

        

            

                1552
            

            

                
            

            

                
            if let Some(parent_did) = parent_map.get(trait_did) {

            

        

            

                1553

                1554

                1555

                1557

                1558
            

            

                
            

            

                
                        .iter()

            

        

            

                1559

                1560
            

            

                
            

            

                
                        .all(|child| child.ident.name == kw::Underscore)

            

        

            

                1561
            

            

                
            

            

                
                {

            

        

            

                1562
            

            

                
            

            

                
                    return false;

            

        

            

                1563
            

            

                
            

            

                
                }

            

        

            

                1564
            

            

                
            

            

                
            }

            

        

            

                1565
            

            

                
            

            

                

            

        

            

                1566
            

            

                
            

            

                
            true

            

        

            

                1567
            

            

                
            

            

                
        });

            

        

            

                1568
            

            

                
            

            

                

            

        

            

                1569

                1570

                1571

                1572
            

            

                
            

            

                

            

        

            

                1573

                1574
            

            

                
            

            

                
            format!("use {};\n", with_crate_prefix!(self.tcx.def_path_str(*trait_did)),)

            

        

            

                1575
            

            

                
            

            

                
        });

            

        

            

                1576
            

            

                
            

            

                

            

        

            

                1577

                1578

                1579
            

            

                
            

            

                
            format!(

            

        

            

                1580
            

            

                
            

            

                
                "use {}::*; // trait {}\n",
